required: time, perl, perl-JSON, mapr utils

1.
copy "mapr" directory to /usr/local/zabbix/etc/ on your main mapr server

2.
file check.mapr.sh:

JAVA_HOME=set your way to java (JAVA_HOME=/usr/java/default by default)
check path to maprcli (/usr/bin/maprcli in file)
you can set permissions for temporary files in this file 

3.
copy or link file userparams_mapr.conf to your "zabbix_agentd.conf.d" directory (/etc/zabbix/zabbix_agentd.conf.d by default)

4.
copy or link file "zabbixmaprcrontab" to /etc/cron.d/

5. 
reload cron (/etc/init.d/crond reload)
reload/restart zabbix_agentd (/etc/init.d/zabbix_agentd reload or /etc/init.d/zabbix-agentd reload or etc)

6.
on zabbix UI 
export mapr_2014.01.28.xml template
